{
  "stem": "25287.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was there a couple hours, even when he gets sick, it was custom was the big synagogue, you saw.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they have a [NON-ENGLISH], what-- what some help to put the new roof from his gran.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he went Sunday, and came home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I supposed to help my uncle at the office, some office work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he came and he said, Zayde want to, you stay with him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I was there till-- if somebody want to have a-- die quietly like that-- this was Sunday.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he said he want to have-- to see all the children, and to live in Bratislava, Czechoslovakia, and [NON-ENGLISH] of the youngest daughter and family.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And once they-- everybody was there, he blessed them, even my two older sisters at that time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I had an uncle, the oldest one, who was very religious, and he said to his father to tell Renea and Margit then blessed, and then they should wear a shawl, too.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He said, no, I just want to they should marry a Jewish boy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was in those age, a very modern-thinking gentleman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "This picture in our dining room, the reason we bought it, because it looked like exactly my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure-- my mother, the nicest holiday-- Shavuos.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I told you when-- and-- oh, I told you we lived in a Gentile neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When was a special Catholic holiday, in front of the Catholic church they put flowers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my mother, we had a big backyard and garden.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when Erev Shavuos, they know that Flora, how they called my mother, going to make the wreath, the crown to the Torah.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we have lots of flowers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And with the children to get to the temple.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
